ce of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6834,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/21\/eating-third-food-drink-air\/","url_meta":{"origin":15269,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Eating: Filling stomach a third for food, drink, air","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 21, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Miqdam ibn Ma\u2019dikarib reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe son of Adam cannot fill a vessel worse than\u00a0his stomach, as\u00a0it is enough\u00a0for him to take a few bites to straighten his back. If he cannot do it, then he may fill it with\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13714,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/04\/24\/sea-water-pure-halal\/","url_meta":{"origin":15269,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Water: Sea water is pure, animals halal to eat","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 24, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, was asked about sea water and he said, \u201cIts water is purifying for ablution,\u00a0and its dead animals are lawful to eat.\u201d Al-Tirmidhi said, \"It is the opinion of most of the jurists among the companions of the Prophet, peace\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":